title: Wisma Ali Bawal Foodcourt - Indian Rice Buffet
typeOfFood: Indian, Buffet, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian food buffet, offers some vegetarian dishes separated from the meat section. Uses tofu in place of paneer. On Friday a vegan biryani is offered instead of the usual rice. Price for a plate is about 6-8RM.
streetAddress: 11, Jalan Tandang, Wisma Ali Bawal Foodcourt
